# Title: File Time Attribute Change - Linux
# Author: Igor Fits, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-15
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect file time attribute change to hide new or changes to existing files.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070.006
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/execve/lnx_auditd_change_file_time_attr.yml

type="EXECVE" "touch" "-t" OR "-acmr" OR "-d" OR "-r"